  "texts": [
    "The inputs for the LLM are the user's statements and the list of candidate service names.",
    "The output from the LLM comprises needs formatted in the 6W1H structure.",
    "During the process of extracting the 6W1H needs, the how element, which represents the service name, is determined.",
    "This allows the true service name desired by the user to be identified from the candidate list.",
    "In other words, with the newly generated service names fromStep 1-1 added to the candidate list, the extraction of user needs related to new services is made possible."
  ],
